  <refsect1>
	<title>Dependencies</title>
	<para>
	  <package>liblod</package> depends upon <package>libcurl</package>,
	  <package>librdf</package>, <package>libxml2</package> and
	  <package>liburi</package>.
	</para>
	<para>
	  A copy of <package>liburi</package> is included in the source
	  distribution.
	</para>
  </refsect1>

